# Entity Skill

## ВёцвфЁ

ВЃѕвАюВџ┤ JPA EntityВЎђ RepositoryвЦ╝ ьћёвАюВаЮьіИ В╗ев▓цВЁўВЌљ вДъЖ▓ї ВъЉВё▒ьЋювІц.

## ВІцьќЅ ВаѕВ░е

### 1. Entity ВъЉВё▒

ВюёВ╣ў: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/{вЈёвЕћВЮИ}/`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "{catalog}", name = "{table_name}")
class EntityName(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    // в╣ёВдѕвІѕВіц ьЋёвЊю
    val userId: String,
    val name: String,

    // Ж┤ђЖ│ё вДцьЋЉ (ьЋёВџћВІю)
    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JoinColumn(name = "category_id", referencedColumnName = "code")
    val category: CategoryEntity? = null,

    // Ж░љВѓг ьЋёвЊю
    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

### 2. Repository ВъЉВё▒

ВюёВ╣ў: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/{вЈёвЕћВЮИ}/`

```kotlin
interface EntityNameRepository : JpaRepository<EntityName, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): List<EntityName>
    fun findByUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): List<EntityName>
}
```

### 3. Catalog ВёаьЃЮ

| Catalog | вЈёвЕћВЮИ |
|---------|--------|
| `maum` | user, profile, call, product, follow |
| `moment` | post, moment, comment, like |
| `chat` | chat_room |
| `notification` | notification, notification_setting |

### 4. В╗┤ьїїВЮ╝ ьЎЋВЮИ

```bash
./gradlew :domain:compileKotlin
```

## ВБ╝ВЮўВѓгьЋГ

- Entityвіћ `var` ВхюВєїьЎћ, в│ђЖ▓й ьЋёВџћьЋю ьЋёвЊювДї `var`
- `@Table`ВЮў `catalog`віћ ВІцВаю DB В╣┤ьЃѕвАюЖиИвфЁЖ│╝ ВЮ╝В╣ў
- `@JoinColumn`ВЮў `referencedColumnName`ВЮё вфЁВІюВаЂВю╝вАю ВДђВаЋ (ЖИ░в│ИЖ░њ `id`Ж░ђ ВЋёвІї Ж▓йВџ░)
- ВќЉв░ЕьќЦ Ж┤ђЖ│ёв│┤вІц вІев░ЕьќЦ Ж┤ђЖ│ё Вџ░Вёа
